{"tid":1703156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想罷工成功嘅同我入黎","createTime":"2019-11-10T06:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T08:33:33.000Z","uid":89006,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b342dc6e459757fb72d03117e9f42625af7d4b73","tid":1703156,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"係抗爭前線戰況直擊睇到ge投稿：<br />\n<br />\n1111嘅行動唔應該叫做罷工，我覺得罷工要做好組織、分析、分配先，罷工原意係咩先，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係想癱瘓政府/社會運作，令政府/香港經濟受損，從而迫政府妥協。</span></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係份份工都適合罷工</span></span></strong>，有d工返去搞亂檔比罷工有更大威力，有d工則唔適合罷工，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要各行各業做好哂分析，分配好、安排好再罷工先會有威力</span></span></strong>。如果唔係就係純粹唔返工，對政府/社會冇咩影響。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">濫用罷工呢個名，會消費左唔熟悉呢樣野嘅人對罷工行動嘅信心。</span></span></strong>好似航空界手足，而家損失慘重，隨時影到下次航空界罷工搞唔成（e.g.佢已經炒左好多黃，請返好多藍）；又例如黃店咁，個人認為佢地唔應該罷工，佢地罷工對政府/經濟冇咩影響，反而佢罷工，手足要食野唔通去藍店食咩。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而1111嘅行動應係朝早周圍塞</span></span></strong>，各位憤怒又唔想返工嘅手足，應該用行動令到其他人（同埋自己）都因交通問題返唔到工；就算有日我地真係搞到罷工，都唔係匿係屋企訓覺啦，自己唔返工容乜易丫，令對家都返唔到工先係關鍵呀！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以1111行動內容為堵塞交通。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n終於有人(鄭立)詳細指出罷工既問題係邊度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693749</a><br />\n<br />\n我係三罷谷主，我有嘢講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1701420/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1701420/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">仲有，1111唔係搞工會ge人搞架，亦都唔係開始無限期三罷。</span></span></strong> <br />\n要罷工有成效，迫到政府妥協，咁就要有準備，唔係話定左邊日罷工，你個日唔番工就得，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而係準備過程你都要積極咁參與，每一個香港人都有責任去籌備罷工</span></span></strong>。籌備罷工係需要一段時間，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想罷得成，就要有耐性</span></span></strong>。 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">宜家有四個工會架啦，分別係金融、保險、IT同公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">想搞工會但搵唔到手足：教育界、黨鐵同物流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知有咩幫到手？入左group就知架啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWDeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=7744dcc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\nGroup List <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F186&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWDeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=588ff184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/186</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWDeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=52f47f97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33hmGRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33hmGRR&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWDeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=0d7baf0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33hmGRR</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">一星期內：</span>三罷channel要過5萬subscribe<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">兩星期內：</span>新四大工會過五千申請（鼓勵新工會每日公佈新增會員人數）<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">三星期內：</span